type: web_research
title: 暗号通貨トレーディング リスク回避・トレード停止シグナルシステム 実装調査
key_insights[10]: "Freqtrade: 最も活発なオープンソース取引bot、custom_stoploss()でATRベースのリスク管理実装可能、Fear&Greed Indexを1D timeframeで統合しBTC FGI>85または<20でaltcoin取引を自動停止する実装例あり","Jesse Trading Bot: 300+インジケーター、リスク管理ツール内蔵、スポット/先物対応、部分約定・ポートフォリオリスク管理機能あり","OctoBot: AI/Grid/DCA/TradingView統合、5.2k stars、Python実装、15+取引所対応","センチメント分析: CryptoBERT(BERT暗号特化)、FinBERT(金融BERT)を活用した実装多数、95%精度達成例あり","Whale Alert: Python/Node.js実装多数、Telegram/Discord統合、Binance/Bitfinex/ETH blockchain監視、リアルタイムWebSocket API利用","Liquidation Cascade: binance-liquidation-tracker(WebSocket)、py-liquidation-map(可視化)、aave-liquidation-model(cascade予測関数)実装あり","オンチェーンデータ: Glassnode公式Python client(非推奨)、CryptoDataPy(統合API推奨)、Santiment sanpy(GraphQL→pandas)実装","Funding Rate: funding-bot(Bitfinex、閾値超過でwebhook alert)、ARBOT(spot-futures arbitrage、15-30%年利)実装","Market Regime: regimetry(教師なし検出)、market_regime_discovery(BTC/ETH/BNB DL)、GARCH volatility clustering実装","NLP Trading: Cryptocurrency-Sentiment-Bot(Vader Lexicon+Reddit)、sentiment-trading-bot(Twitter/Reddit/News)、nlp-sentiment-quant-monitor(FinBERT+RSS)"
findings[10]: "Freqtrade: custom_stoploss()でATR動的ストップロス、adjust_trade_position()でDCAリスク管理、FixedRiskRewardLoss戦略実装済み","Fear&Greed統合: alternative.me API、1日1回更新、CSVキャッシュ推奨、FGI>85/FGI<20で緊急停止実装例あり","Whale監視: crypto-whale-watcher(Binance/Bitfinex volume alert)、crypto-whales-tracking-bot(ETH/BTC whale IN/OUT)、simple-big-whale-alert-bot(Discord統合)","Liquidation追跡: binance-liquidation-tracker(WebSocket、最小金額/ticker filter)、ccip-liquidation-protector(Chainlink Automation)実装","センチメントbot: sentiment-analysis-crypto(DistilBERT 95%精度)、Twitter_Activated_Crypto_Trading_Bot(keyword 1秒執行)、AI-Powered-PumpBot(Twitter/Telegram/Discord NLP)","MVRV/NUPL: crypto_bot_project_2(LSTM+MVRV+NUPL for BTC/USD prediction)実装例、Glassnodeデータ統合可能","Funding Rate監視: instabot42/funding-bot(閾値超過でwebhook→Alertatron/IFTTT/Zapier)、複数DEX間arbitrage実装","Market Regime: kjpou1/regimetry(教師なし時系列検出)、trungminhdo4/market_regime_discovery(DL、BTC/ETH/BNB)、Crypto-Strategy-Lab(spectral complexity)","オンチェーンAPI: Glassnode公式client非推奨、CryptoDataPy推奨(統合interface)、Santiment sanpy(GraphQL)実装","CCXT統合: ZTOM(Trade Order Management SDK、CCXT上の失敗耐性layer)、stop loss実装課題多数(Binance trailing stop等)"
techniques:
  "Risk Management": "custom_stoploss(ATR-based), adjust_trade_position(DCA), portfolio-level risk calculation"
  "Sentiment Analysis": "FinBERT/CryptoBERT(HuggingFace), Vader Lexicon, Twitter/Reddit/News RSS feed"
  "Fear&Greed Integration": "alternative.me API, 1D timeframe, CSV cache, FGI>85/<20 threshold"
  "Whale Detection": "WebSocket API(Binance/Bitfinex), volume threshold filter, IN/OUT transaction tracking"
  "Liquidation Tracking": "WebSocket forced liquidation feed, cascade prediction model, Chainlink Automation"
  "On-chain Data": "CryptoDataPy(unified API), Glassnode/Santiment client, MVRV/NUPL/SOPR indicators"
  "Funding Rate": "Webhook alert(threshold exceeded), spot-futures arbitrage, multi-exchange comparison"
  "Market Regime": "Unsupervised clustering, GARCH volatility model, spectral complexity, DL-based state detection"
  "Alert Delivery": "Telegram Bot API, Discord webhook, LINE Notify, IFTTT/Zapier integration"
  Backtesting: "Freqtrade/Jesse engine, historical FGI data, parameter optimization, paper trading"
